CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 16, 1964, pg. 8, reads: "Cutting Cake - Mr. and Mrs. Frederick Stanford cut their wedding cake, following their marriage on May 9. The bride is the former Mrs. Mary Finks."
TitMainTitle: Groom Frederick Stanford wearing bow tie and jacket with satin lapels, and bride Mary Finks Stanford, wearing tiara and floral dress, posed in interior in front of light colored curtain
